summit in a bid to yield positive results that can consolidate
Arab unity.
</P>
<P>
The summit that Arafat has called for is intended to unify Arab
stances on the stalled Middle East peace process and the
challenges the Arab nation faces.
</P>
<P>
Saleh reiterated Yemen's backing for Palestinian people's
struggle to restore their legitimate rights and establish an
independent state with Jerusalem as the capital.
</P>
