The two leaders discussed issues related to the deadlock of the
peace process due to the intransigence and extremism of the
Israeli government.
</P>
<P>
Peace talks between the Palestinians and Israelis came to a
halt in March 1997 when Israel began building a Jewish housing
unit in traditionally Arab East Jerusalem. 
