NATO "will be looking very carefully at these options, because
you can't consider military options without the most detailed form
of planning in this part of the world," he added.
</P>
<P>
The British Defense chief also noted that Kosovo crisis would
be at the top of the agenda of the NATO defense ministers meeting
due to be held in Brussels next week.  
