breathe fresh air.
</P>
<P>
Professor Yuan-Cheng B. Fung, with the University of California,
San Diego, said the human society is now being ruled by the
utilitarianism at the turn of the century, and the intellectual
circle should carry forward the national tradition of shouldering
the historic task.
</P>
<P>
