<HEADLINE> Xinhua Stock Indexes Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 5 (Xinhua) -- Today's Xinhua A stock index
dropped by 0.58 point to close at 171.35, while the Xinhua B stock
index edged down 0.70 point to finish at 45.87.
</P>
<P>
The Xinhua Stock index is China's first national unitary stock
exponent, which is jointly designed and issued by the Economic
Information Department of the Xinhua News Agency and Beijing
University.  
