<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, June 5 (Xinhua) -- The Nigerian National Drug Law
Enforcement Agency (NDLEA) has discovered 25 suspected Indian
hemp farms in Delta State in the south and arrested 12 persons
believed to be their owners.
</P>
