<HEADLINE> City in Central China Trying to Improve Investment Environment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZHENGZHOU, June 5 (Xinhua) -- Better investment environment is
always important for overseas investors in the city of Zhengzhou,
Mayor Chen Yichu said recently.
</P>
<P>
Zhengzhou, capital of central China's Henan Province, has a
complaint hot-line for overseas investors, and has decided to give
special protection to 96 overseas-financed enterprises, which can
air their grievances during an monthly overseas investment
coordination meeting.
</P>
<P>
