and society must make more efforts in environmental protection, he
said.
</P>
<P>
The units across the country were also given prizes yesterday
for their key role in helping carry out environmental awareness
activities.
</P>
<P>
Through these activities, women nationwide are taught to avoid
throwing garbage into rivers and lakes, to plant trees in their
neighborhood, and to use cloth bags instead of thin plastic
bags. 
