<HEADLINE> Tianjin to Exhibit Patented Technology, Products </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, June 5 (Xinhua) -- An exhibition of patented
technology and products will be held in this north China port city
June 10-14.
</P>
<P>
Most noteworthy of the exhibition is the presence of a large
number of private and township enterprises who will put their
technology on the show.
</P>
<P>
The exhibition, jointly sponsored by the State Intellectual
Property Rights Bureau and the Tianjin Municipal Government, is
being held in response to the development trend of the age of
information and the knowledge economy, according to experts.
</P>
<P>
