<HEADLINE> China's Investment in Western Area up from February to March </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 5 (Xinhua) -- The latest figures from the State
Statistics Bureau show that China's investment in its western
area hit 22.8 billion yuan in the first three months of 1998, up
