be careful and to avoid large demonstrations and crowds.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, employees of the U.S. embassy in Jakarta and the
U.S. consulate in Surabaya who were evacuated last month will not
return back at present "until the security situation further
stabilizes," the State Department said. 
