<HEADLINE> World Bank Finances Nicaragua Road Project </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, June 4 (Xinhua) -- The World Bank approved here
Thursday an interest-free credit of 47.4 million U.S. dollars
equivalent to help Nicaragua in its road rehabilitation and
maintenance project.
